{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MathML: Deriving the Quadratic Formula","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Examples/Deriving_the_Quadratic_Formula","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","hasMathML":true,"sidebarHTML":"\n    <ol>\n        <li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element\">MathML Reference</a></strong>\n\n        \n            </li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\">&lt;math&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\">&lt;menclose&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/merror\">&lt;merror&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\">&lt;mpadded&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom\">&lt;mphantom&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot\">&lt;mroot&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow\">&lt;mrow&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\">&lt;ms&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt\">&lt;msqrt&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\">&lt;mstyle&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\">&lt;munderover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/semantics\">&lt;semantics&gt;</a></li>\n        \n\n        \n    </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>本页概述了二次方程式的推导过程。</p>\n\n<p><math><mtable columnalign=\"left\"><mtr><mtd><mrow>我们取一般形式的二次方程，并解出 x：<mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace></mrow></mtd></mtr></mtable></math></p>\n\n<p><math><mtable columnalign=\"left\"><mtr><mtd><mrow><mrow><mrow><mrow> <mi>a</mi> <mo>⁢</mo> <msup> <mi>x</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup></mrow> <mo> + </mo> <mi>b</mi> <mo>⁢</mo> <mi>x</mi> </mrow> <mo> + </mo> <mi>c</mi> </mrow> <mo>=</mo> <mn>0</mn> </mrow> </mtd> </mtr> <mtr> <mtd> <mrow> <mrow> <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace> <mi>a</mi> <mo>⁢</mo> <msup> <mi>x</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup></mrow> <mo> + </mo> <mi>b</mi> <mo>⁢</mo> <mi>x</mi> <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace> </mrow> <mo>=</mo> <mo>-</mo><mi> c</mi><mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace> </mtd> </mtr> <mtr> <mtd> <mrow> <mrow> <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace> <msup> <mi>x</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup></mrow> <mo> + </mo> <mfrac> <mrow> <mi>b</mi> </mrow> <mi>a</mi> </mfrac> <mo>⁤</mo> <mi>x</mi> </mrow> <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace> <mo>=</mo> <mfrac> <mrow> <mo>-</mo><mi>c</mi> </mrow> <mi>a</mi> </mfrac> <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2ex\"></mspace><mrow><mtext mathcolor=\"red\" mathsize=\"10pt\">Divide out leading coefficient.</mtext> </mrow> </mtd> </mtr> <mtr> <mtd> <mrow> <mrow> <mrow> <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace> <msup> <mi>x</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup></mrow> <mo> + </mo> <mfrac> <mrow> <mi>b</mi> </mrow> <mi>a</mi> </mfrac> <mo>⁤</mo> <mi>x</mi> <mo> + </mo> <msup> <mfenced> <mfrac> <mrow> <mi>b</mi> </mrow> <mrow> <mn>2</mn> <mi>a</mi> </mrow> </mfrac> </mfenced> <mn>2</mn> </msup> </mrow> <mo>=</mo> <mfrac> <mrow> <mo>-</mo> <mi>c</mi> <mo>(</mo> <mn>4</mn> <mi>a</mi> <mo>)</mo> </mrow> <mrow> <mi>a</mi> <mo>(</mo> <mn>4</mn> <mi>a</mi> <mo>)</mo> </mrow></mfrac> </mrow> <mo> + </mo> <mfrac> <mrow> <msup> <mi>b</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> </mrow> <mrow> <mn>4</mn> <msup> <mi>a</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> </mrow></mfrac> <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2ex\"></mspace><mrow><mtext mathcolor=\"red\" mathsize=\"10pt\">Complete the square.</mtext> </mrow> </mtd> </mtr> <mtr> <mtd> <mrow> <mrow> <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace> <mo>(</mo> <mi>x</mi> <mo> + </mo> <mfrac> <mrow> <mi>b</mi> </mrow> <mrow> <mn>2</mn> <mi>a</mi> </mrow></mfrac> <mo>)</mo> <mo>(</mo> <mi>x</mi> <mo> + </mo> <mfrac> <mrow> <mi>b</mi> </mrow> <mrow> <mn>2</mn> <mi>a</mi> </mrow></mfrac> <mo>)</mo> <mo>=</mo> <mfrac> <mrow> <msup> <mi>b</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> <mo> - </mo> <mn>4</mn> <mi>a</mi> <mi>c</mi> </mrow> <mrow> <mn>4</mn> <msup> <mi>a</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> </mrow></mfrac> </mrow> <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2ex\"></mspace><mrow><mtext mathcolor=\"red\" mathsize=\"10pt\">Discriminant revealed.</mtext> </mrow> </mrow> </mtd> </mtr> <mtr> <mtd> <mrow> <mrow> <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace> <msup> <mrow> <mo>(</mo> <mi>x</mi> <mo> + </mo> <mfrac> <mrow> <mi>b</mi> </mrow> <mrow> <mn>2</mn> <mi>a</mi> </mrow></mfrac> <mo>)</mo> </mrow> <mn>2</mn> </msup> <mo>=</mo> <mfrac> <mrow> <msup> <mi>b</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> <mo> - </mo> <mn>4</mn> <mi>a</mi> <mi>c</mi> </mrow> <mrow> <mn>4</mn> <msup> <mi>a</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> </mrow></mfrac> </mrow> <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2ex\"></mspace><mrow><mtext mathcolor=\"red\" mathsize=\"10pt\"></mtext> </mrow> </mrow> </mtd> </mtr> <mtr> <mtd> <mrow> <mrow> <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace> <mrow> <mi>x</mi> <mo> + </mo> <mfrac> <mrow> <mi>b</mi> </mrow> <mrow> <mn>2</mn> <mi>a</mi> </mrow></mfrac> </mrow> <mo>=</mo> <msqrt> <mfrac> <mrow> <msup> <mi>b</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> <mo> - </mo> <mn>4</mn> <mi>a</mi> <mi>c</mi> </mrow> <mrow> <mn>4</mn> <msup> <mi>a</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> </mrow></mfrac> </msqrt> </mrow> <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2ex\"></mspace><mrow><mtext mathcolor=\"red\" mathsize=\"10pt\"></mtext> </mrow> </mrow> </mtd> </mtr> <mtr> <mtd> <mrow> <mrow> <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace> <mrow> <mi>x</mi> </mrow> <mo>=</mo> <mfrac> <mrow> <mo>-</mo><mi>b</mi> </mrow> <mrow> <mn>2</mn> <mi>a</mi> </mrow></mfrac> <mo>±</mo><mrow><mo>{</mo><mi>C</mi><mo>}</mo></mrow> <msqrt> <mfrac> <mrow> <msup> <mi>b</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> <mo> - </mo> <mn>4</mn> <mi>a</mi> <mi>c</mi> </mrow> <mrow> <mn>4</mn> <msup> <mi>a</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> </mrow></mfrac> </msqrt> </mrow> <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2ex\"></mspace><mrow><mtext mathcolor=\"red\" mathsize=\"10pt\">There's the vertex formula.</mtext> </mrow> </mrow> </mtd> </mtr> <mtr> <mtd> <mrow> <mrow> <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2.5ex\"></mspace> <mrow> <mi>x</mi> </mrow> <mo>=</mo> <mfrac> <mrow> <mo>-</mo> <mi> b</mi> <mo>±</mo><mrow><mo>{</mo><mi>C</mi><mo>}</mo></mrow> <msqrt> <msup> <mi>b</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> <mo> - </mo> <mn>4</mn> <mi>a</mi> <mi>c</mi> </msqrt></mrow> <mrow> <mn>2</mn> <mi>a</mi> </mrow></mfrac> </mrow> <mspace depth=\"1ex\" height=\"0.5ex\" width=\"2ex\"></mspace> <mrow><mtext mathcolor=\"red\" mathsize=\"10pt\"></mtext> </mrow> </mrow> </mtd> </mtr> </mtable></math></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"本页概述了二次方程式的推导过程。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Lösungsformel für die Quadratische Gleichung","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"MathML: Deriving the Quadratic Formula","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"MathML: Dériver la formule quadratique","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"MathML: 二次方程式の解の公式を導く","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"MathML: Вывод Квадратичной Формулы","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/mathml/examples/deriving_the_quadratic_formula","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/mathml/examples/deriving_the_quadratic_formula/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML","title":"MathML"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Examples","title":"举个例子"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Examples/Deriving_the_Quadratic_Formula","title":"MathML: Deriving the Quadratic Formula"}],"pageTitle":"MathML: Deriving the Quadrati